org.sikuli.script

Class Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sikuli.script.Region
      • org.sikuli.script.Match
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Match>

    public class Match
extends Region
implements java.lang.Comparable<Match>
    holds the result of a find operation, is itself the region on the screen, where the image was found and hence inherits all methods from Region.
    attributes:
    the match score (0 ... 1.0)
    the click target (e.g. from Pattern)
    a ref to the image used for search
    or the text used for find text
    and elapsed times for debugging
